flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    CDN[CDN Edge<br/>popular prefixes]
    App[Autocomplete<br/>App Service]
    Shard1[Trie Shard 1]
    ShardN[Trie Shard N]
    Logs[(Query Log<br/>event stream)]
    Aggregator[Aggregator +<br/>Top-K Builder]
    Snapshot[(Trie Snapshot<br/>Object Store)]

    Client -->|prefix| CDN
    CDN -.->|miss| App
    CDN -->|cached top-k| Client
    App -->|prefix route| Shard1
    App -->|prefix route| ShardN
    Logs -.->|hourly| Aggregator
    Aggregator --> Snapshot
    Snapshot -.->|atomic swap| Shard1
    Snapshot -.->|atomic swap| ShardN

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class CDN,App,Aggregator service
    class Shard1,ShardN,Logs,Snapshot store
